    <S id="S_0">
        <FORM>iakay kudra tangea kudra tatama la kikamadhamadha la parakay ki karadrare.</FORM>
        <TRANSL xml:lang="zh"> 有一位老先生在用竹籃子摘芒果。</TRANSL>
