    <S id="S_9">
        <FORM>la dreele kuini tatama si alau amani kay lalasu kuini wamalra kuini kamadha li aiya.</FORM>
        <TRANSL xml:lang="zh"> 老先生看了就說，可能是那幾個男生拿了我的芒果。</TRANSL>
        <TRANSL xml:lang="en"> The old man looked (at them) and said maybe they were the ones who took my mango.</TRANSL>
